<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4636246>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Moniligaster keralensis Narayanan & Julka sp. nov. A. Ventral view. B. Prostate of right hand side, dorsal view. C. Prostatic capsule of right hand side, dorsal view. D. Spermatheca of left hand side. Abbreviations. M.H.L.—Mass of hairpin loops; Oe.—Oesophagus; Pr.C.—Prostatic capsule; Pr.—Prostate; Pr.D.—Prostatic duct; Sep.—Septum; Sp.A.—Spermathecal ampulla; Sp.Atr.G.—Spermathecal atrial gland; Sp.D.—Spermathecal duct; S.M.A.—Secondary male aperture; Sp.P.—Spermathecal pore; T.S.—Testis sac; Vd—Vas deferens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4636246/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4636250>
